## Note: This file has been split into focused rule files

The coding patterns have been organized into the following focused rule files:

- **code-style.mdc** - General code style guidelines
- **database-schema.mdc** - Database setup, migrations, table definitions, SQL patterns, and @FetchAll/@FetchOne
- **feature-structure.mdc** - Feature file organization pattern (reducer + view in same file)
- **reducer-patterns.mdc** - Reducer structure, composition, effects, and delegate patterns
- **state-management.mdc** - ObservableState, IdentifiedArrayOf, and focus state management
- **view-patterns.mdc** - ViewAction, bindable stores, scoping, and presentation patterns
- **testing.mdc** - Testing strategies and patterns
- **dependencies.mdc** - Dependency management and client patterns
- **navigation.mdc** - Navigation and dismissal patterns
- **utilities.mdc** - Common utilities and helpers
- **best-practices.mdc** - Best practices summary

All these files are set to `alwaysApply: true`, so they will all be automatically applied.
